body_html:
Inception-v3 may now run on batches of arbitrary size by using the newly released code here:
https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/inception

In particular, one can adapt this script to accept arbitrary data sets:
https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/inception/imagenet_eval.py
